OL,3,CCarer admits neglect of resident who
OL,4,Cdied after medication mix-up
OL,6,FA care home worker has admitted
OL,7,Fneglect of a resident who died after
OL,8,Fshe gave him someone else's medication.
OL,10,FJane Barnard, 66, denies killing Derek
OL,11,FDavies, 75, who lived at the care home
OL,12,Fwhere she was employed and died on
OL,13,FSeptember 8 2021.
OL,15,FAt Gloucester Crown Court on Monday 24
OL,16,FNovember, she pleaded guilty to a
OL,17,Fsecond charge that she wilfully
OL,18,Fneglected Mr Davies between September
OL,19,F5 and September 9 that year by failing
OL,20,Fto disclose she had wrongfully
OL,21,Fadministered morphine.
