OL,3,CCarer admits neglect of resident who
OL,4,Cdied after medication mix-up
OL,6,FBarnard, of Longlevens, Gloucester,
OL,7,Fwas employed as a care worker at
OL,8,FWheatridge Court in Abbeydale,
OL,9,FGloucester, where Mr Davies was a
OL,10,Fresident when he died.
OL,12,FThe court heard that on the morning of
OL,13,FSeptember 6, Barnard erroneously gave
OL,14,Fhim medication prescribed for another
OL,15,Fpatient, Jason Dodsworth.
OL,17,FThe medication she gave Mr Davies
OL,18,Fincluded 90mg of slow-release morphine.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
