OL,3,CCarer admits neglect of resident who
OL,4,Cdied after medication mix-up
OL,6,FAlexandra Healy KC, prosecuting, said:
OL,7,F"When she realised her mistake, which
OL,8,Fshe did shortly afterwards, rather
OL,9,Fthan report it immediately, which she
OL,10,Fshould have done so that urgent
OL,11,Fmedical advice could be obtained, she
OL,12,Fnot only told nobody, but she covered
OL,13,Fher tracks to conceal what she had
OL,14,Fdone.
OL,16,F"She concealed and disposed of the
OL,17,Fmedication she should have given him
OL,18,Fthat morning... she claimed she had
OL,19,Faccidentally dropped Mr Dodsworth's
OL,20,Fmedication down the sink."
