OL,3,CCarer admits neglect of resident who
OL,4,Cdied after medication mix-up
OL,6,FMs Healy told the court: "The
OL,7,Fdefendant kept saying, 'I can't
OL,8,Fbelieve what I've done, I just
OL,9,Fpanicked.'"
OL,11,FWhen the care home contacted the
OL,12,Fhospital, it was confirmed Mr Davies
OL,13,Fhad died that morning.
OL,15,FThe original cause of death was
OL,16,Fdocumented as a brainstem stroke but
OL,17,Fit was later understood Mr Davies'
OL,18,Factual cause of death was a
OL,19,Fconsequence of morphine toxicity.
