OL,3,CCarer admits neglect of resident who
OL,4,Cdied after medication mix-up
OL,6,FAt the time of the incident, Barnard
OL,7,Fhad been employed as a care worker at
OL,8,FWheatridge Court for 32 years.
OL,10,FMs Healy said: "Had she not
OL,11,Fadministered him with that morphine or
OL,12,Fhad she reported promptly, when she
OL,13,Frealised what she had done, Mr Davies
OL,14,Fwould not have died.
OL,16,F"Her breaches of her duty of care to
OL,17,FMr Davies were so serious that the
OL,18,Fprosecution say they are properly
OL,19,Fcharacterised as criminal."
OL,21,FThe trial continues.
